article_title: St. John's cutting 43 management jobs, citing reduced reimbursements, ACA

article_metadata.description: The 43 jobs St. John's Hospital eliminated Thursday were part of an effort to avoid harming care “at the bedside” while coping with reduced payments.
article_metadata.author: Dean Olsen Staff Writer
